						<summary>

						<p>Stone set up near the Hanumān temple.</p>						

						<p>[Kanna]radēva A.D. 1260.</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription is dated in the 15th year of the reign of [Kanna]radēva, Raudri, Bhādrapada ba. 14, Sunday, corresponding to A.D. 1260, September 5, Sunday f.d.t. 08.</p>						

						<p>It records the death of a person in a fight. Mentions Yaḷeyasirivura.</p>						

						</summary>
